headline: Liberty Energy Inc. Appoints Alice Yake (Jackson) to Its Board of Directors
summary: DENVER, October 16, 2025--Liberty Energy Inc. (NYSE: LBRT; "Liberty" or the "Company") announced today the appointment of Alice Yake (Jackson) to its Board of Directors.

headline: Wildfire Settlements and Grid Investments Could Be a Game Changer for Xcel Energy (XEL)
summary: In recent weeks, Xcel Energy finalized comprehensive settlements totaling US$640 million related to the 2021 Marshall Fire in Colorado, with US$350 million covered by insurance, while also receiving regulatory approval for a US$1.9 billion wildfire mitigation plan in Colorado and a US$500 million resiliency plan in Texas. These developments significantly reduce legal uncertainties and liability risk for Xcel, while reinforcing the company's focus on grid resiliency and supporting its...
